---
import { correctionUrl } from '../utils/site';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Florida Property Tax Tracker" description="Purpose, neutrality policy, and correction policy for Florida Property Tax Tracker.">
  <div class="shell page-intro">
    <p class="terminal-label">&gt; about</p>
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>Florida Property Tax Tracker is a neutral civic tracking project for Florida's 2026 property tax elimination proposals and materially related reforms.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="shell prose-grid">
    <section class="section-block">
      <h2>Neutrality Policy</h2>
      <p>The tracker does not endorse or oppose any proposal. It separates official records from stakeholder positions and preserves historical status when proposals change.</p>
      <h2 id="corrections">Correction Policy</h2>
      <p>A correction request should identify the claim being challenged, provide a source URL or document, describe the requested correction, and label the source type.</p>
      <p><a class="text-link" href={correctionUrl}>Submit a correction with a source</a></p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
